{"type": "article", "id": 37525, "title": "想测试下自己的音乐知识？可以看看这张世界地图｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-06T23:03:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32873, "name": "OTHR"}, {"id": 37394, "name": "Zinteh"}, {"id": 18808, "name": "Dorothy"}, {"id": 30214, "name": "Saif Faisal"}, {"id": 37395, "name": "Andrés Guerrero"}, {"id": 37396, "name": "Andrea Minini"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 288, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170206214628e7uw28sYnDVzdGph.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The World Song Map by Dorothy</h3><p>在把地图做得更有趣这件事上，之前就有设计师把音乐和地理结合在一起，创作了<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/20447.html\">以音乐界代表人物为主题的纽约地图</a>。今天要介绍的 The World Song Map 则把音乐的疆域扩大到了整个世界，英国的 <a href=\"http://www.wearedorothy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dorothy</a> 工作室耗时八个月的时间进行策划，将国家、地区和城市都替换成了相关歌曲名，比如地图上的俄罗斯就改为披头士的著名歌曲《Back in the USSR》。除了一些比较常规的标记之外，设计师也没有忘记山河湖海，以至于这张地图最终涵盖了超过一千首歌曲——虽然看起来密密麻麻的，但这种涨知识的方式还挺有趣。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.wearedorothy.com/shop/category/world-maps\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这张地图，它分为经典版和单色印刷的复古版两种，售价分别为 25 和 35 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214701lSXUzTjbLNChKDMw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214702TXQ5o3dv2F9r78HS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214702AUN0wgI7Hk9DzsWS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702062147020JCeKLvrNqYz2ZUc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214703xrjqmS3NDo7aAcH5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fravel by Aili Jian</h3><p>厌倦了四四方方千篇一律的行李箱？不妨来看看美国设计师 Aili Jian 带领的团队以“陪伴你一起上路的宠物”为概念设计的 Fravel。这款号称世界上最可爱的行李箱有一双醒目的“耳朵”，通过内置的感应器，当你抚摸行李箱时，它们就会摇晃起来和你进行互动，底部的磁吸意味着耳朵可以根据需要随时拆卸安装。当你带着行李箱出门时，它正面右下角的心形灯还会模拟心跳闪烁起来。在这些和可爱挂钩的要素之外，行李箱本身也设有 USB 充电插口和隐蔽式口袋这类实用的功能。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1789392299/fravel-the-worlds-cutest-suitcase\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 269 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702062147274zrOiTu2hlot6eNQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214728OUqk2FaTo0ICs5Yn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214729ildyHGTtBUXhrPea.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214729ainwD1d9WzUpIvjr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214728jopDRF9Sn6L1xCte.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>3D Illusion Lamps by Zinteh</h3><p>利用视觉错觉得当，生活中平凡的物件也能让人眼前一亮。成立于 2011 年的 Zinteh 是一间来自保加利亚的灯具公司，旗下的灯饰造型都很有“欺诈性”，每一块亚克力平板都经过精心设计，模糊了 2D 和 3D 之间的界限。得益于平板式设计，安装和运输也变得更加方便。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Zinteh\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 210 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214752iEdK7zchB1U3DOqy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679231\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214752OIkEUZGgpYCDjqi8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214752MLQom41cXA6En7lN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.816000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214752Y5uT3sPaKvgpLU9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Loup Fruit Bowl by Saif Faisal</h3><p>第一眼看到这件名为 Loup 的陶瓷制品时，你或许很难猜到它的作用。这个环状容器实际上是印度设计师 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saif Faisal</a> 以传统的水果碗为原型设计的，由 3D 打印设计品牌 <a href=\"https://www.othr.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTHR</a> 负责生产。除了摆放水果之外，它简洁的外型留给了人们足够的想象空间，探索更多的用途。Loup 是一款限量产品，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.othr.com/products/loup\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为 65 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214813ZQsM2gkmNKF7eWjo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214813NwAqZIKoJV8W965v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592528\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214814V9uHNbKDCXeBUQkh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017020621481375jo8zkVgTt3ULsR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Abeeja Honey by Andrés Guerrero</h3><p>Abeeja Honey 是西班牙穆尔西亚一个小型的蜂蜜生产商，为了帮助这个小品牌尽可能多地吸引到消费者的目光，平面设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/aannddeerr\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andrés Guerrero</a> 为它设计了一个看似极简实则暗藏玄机的包装。透明罐头外围绕着一圈黄底黑字的标签，顶部的封条也选用了黑色，都是容易让人联想到蜜蜂的设计。Guerero 还在标签左右两侧预留了切口，只要轻轻一抠，原本朴素的黄色罐子就变成一个展翅的小蜜蜂了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702062149226OsAKTg52pHx73iM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702062149249ZpYLnlsHJkreqNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214922ENXQU4q0VhLvoDJ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702062149221c9TGF0MpLqtSBvH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Architectural illustrations by Andrea Minini</h3><p>拍摄屏幕类物体时，照片上常常会出现像是水波一样的条纹，看起来有点碍眼。不过你有没有想过它们其实也可以变成一种艺术？最近擅长利用这种波纹进行创作的意大利艺术家 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/andreaminini\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andrea Minini</a> 受创意机构 <a href=\"http://studioverde.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studioverde</a> 的委托，为建材供应商 <a href=\"http://www.progressprofiles.com/italian/index.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Progress Profiles</a> 设计了 13 幅精致的黑白<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43080389/Architectural-illustrations-Progress-Profiles\" rel=\"nofollow\">建筑图</a>。Minini 仔细研究了这 13 座世界知名建筑的结构，用一道道白色的波纹将它们的结构化繁为简，同时又不会让人难以辨认。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214845fRONCS137L6oP5IW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214846f5Awvx2IyDi9euEG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214847TCm3fsEoLaAKR4D6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214847GH2PhwuAKgzR3i87.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206214851G9tyV7jHDBI4KN3Q.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.637500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}